ActStrengthening Canadian Citizenship Act
SubjectOrder Fixing June 11, 2015 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing June 11, 2015, as the day on which (1) subsections 2(2), (3), (5), (6), (8), (11), (15) and (17) to (19), 3(1), (2), (4) to (6) and (8) and 4(2), (3), (5), (6), (8), (10) and (11), section 6, subsections 9(2) and (4), section 10, subsection 12(2), section 15, subsections 16(1) and (3), sections 17 and 18, subsections 19(1) and (3), section 23 subsections 24(1) to (5), (5.2) and (6) and sections 25, 26 and 28 to 30 of the STRENGTHENING CANADIAN CITIZENSHIP ACT, chapter 22 of the Statutes of Canada 2014, COME INTO FORCE.
